                            <comment id="14195390" author="gchanan" created="Mon, 3 Nov 2014 23:50:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Which way would you go, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=markrmiller%40gmail.com&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;markrmiller@gmail.com&quot;&gt;markrmiller@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;?  ZkCredentialProvider or ZkCredentialsProvider?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
